content:
Import usage data from an external source to the Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management app to show usage metrics in relevant dashboards.

Create a CSV file with these fields, in this order:
AccountId (Text)
Product2Id (Text)
Year (Text)
Month (Text)
Days (Text)
Hours_Usage (Numeric)
Sessions (Numeric)
Failed_Sessions (Numeric)

Save the CSV file and create the app. See Create and Share the Analytics for Subscriber Lifecycle Management App.

Open the app, click Datasets, locate the Media_Usage dataset, click Edit, Replace Data, Select a file, and upload the CSV file. The next time the dataflow runs, CRM Analytics adds Media_Usage to relevant dashboards.
title: Importing Usage Data to CRM Analytics App
